{"title":"Sublime Text 4 Build 4126 注册","uid":"6754f0b29b50c9f0a557c7abad9ed9ee","slug":"Sublime-Text-4-Build-4126-注册","date":"2022-01-24T04:04:28.000Z","updated":"2022-01-24T04:30:00.927Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Sublime-Text-4-Build-4126-注册.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"1-修改host\"><a href=\"#1-修改host\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.修改host\"></a>1.修改host</h2><p>找到 “C:\\Windows\\System32\\drivers\\etc\\hosts” ,添加:</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">127.0.0.1 license.**sublime**hq.com # SublimeText \n\n127.0.0.1 www.sublimetext.com # SublimeText</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"2-HxD工具修改sub-lime-exe值\"><a href=\"#2-HxD工具修改sub-lime-exe值\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.HxD工具修改sub_lime.exe值\"></a>2.HxD工具修改sub_lime.exe值</h2><p>使用HxD工具修改sub_lime.exe值（<a href=\"https://hexed.it/%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E6%9B%BF%E6%8D%A2%E5%AE%8C%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%8E%E8%A6%81%E5%8F%A6%E5%AD%98%E4%B8%BA%EF%BC%8C%E6%9B%BF%E6%8D%A2%E5%8E%9F%E6%9D%A5%E4%B8%BB%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%88%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97%E4%B8%BA%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82sub_lime.exe%EF%BC%89\">https://hexed.it/），注意替换完之后要另存为，替换原来主程序（名字为安装程序的主程序名字，如sub_lime.exe）</a>. 搜索替换对应本版本的值:</p>\n<p>第一步:</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">x64:\nSearch for: 4157415656575553B828210000  \nReplace with: 33C0FEC0C3575553B828210000\nx86:\nSearch for: 55535756B8AC200000\nReplace with: 33C0FEC0C3AC200000</code></pre>\n\n<p>第二步:</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">Search for: 6C6963656E73652E7375626C696D6568712E636F6D\nReplace with: 7375626C696D6568712E6C6F63616C686F73740000</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"3-打开sublime-输入注册码完成注册\"><a href=\"#3-打开sublime-输入注册码完成注册\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.打开sublime,输入注册码完成注册:\"></a>3.打开sublime,输入注册码完成注册:</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-no